Package author: Igor Gaponenko

Please describe any modifications that you made to the package in the
reverse time order.

Tag: V00-00-08
2015-07-29 Igor Gaponenko
- refactored the project to make it easier for deployment as a single
ZIP file w/o moving any files around or changing their content. Moved
in and properly modified external classes (and relevant CSS) which lived
before in a separate PCDS-specific package 'webfwk'
- got rif of PHP procesing of the main index file
- added support for Murali's custom template processor in the index file
- added processing index file query options in JavaScript. This includes
support for up to 5 PVs and optional time range (not used yet) and
a persistent configuration name (not used yet).

Tag: V00-00-07
2015-07-29 Igor Gaponenko
- the 'LIVE' mode
- an option for downloading a table as an CSV document
- an option for downloading (taking a snapshot) of the timeseries plot area
- linear/log10 switch option directly on the timeseries plot

Tag: V00-00-06
2015-07-16 Igor Gaponenko
- finished the protorype version to be given to Murali

